<!-- LANG:EN, title="Why is there no app?"-->

inventaire.io is what we call a [https://tools.wmflabs.org/hub/Q189210 web app]: a website that tries hard to give a great experience on all devices, using the [https://tools.wmflabs.org/hub/Q1153289 web standards] . ([https://github.com/inventaire/inventaire-client/issues/91 Follow our progresses in that direction])

Pros:

* Less work for the developers, meaning that we can give more time to other features
* Future-proof: the web is made of solid standards, and is here to stay! The same can't really be said of the proprietary platforms that are the Apple App Store and Google Play.

Cons:

* The web app does feel less &quot;native&quot;

